### LightKer alpha release v0.2

Notes:
1) LightKer requires a GPU with (at least) two CUDA engines to work properly
- Currently (developed and) supported on NVIDIA GTX980
- Currently developed on Linux
2) To run EXAMPLE1, simply go to '<LK_ROOT>/apps/example1' folder and type
  $ make clean all ## You must have nvcc and all of the required inclusions in your path
	
	To run, type
	$ ./example1




- Mail paolo.burgio@unimore.it for any comment/request